# Frontend environment variables
# Copy to .env.local and set values. Never commit .env.local.
#
# Server-only (no NEXT_PUBLIC_): available only in API routes, Server Components, server actions.
# Client-exposed (NEXT_PUBLIC_): only for values safe to be visible in the browser.
#
# Example when adding env vars:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
# API_SECRET=                    # server-only, required in production
